{"tid":435470,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋覺得麥記最好食係邊三個包?","createTime":"2017-10-14T10:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T11:20:20.000Z","uid":104658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3621d20745c66d8764315dc7a5ee4d56a07c0455","tid":435470,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"唔計餐 唔計麥趣飯 個d <br />\n<br />\n出過無再出 絕版包 其他國家有得食嘅包 都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n汁  餡  肉  菜  醬  芝士 塊包皮  夾黎最好食嘅<br />\n<br />\n講三個你哋鍾意食嘅包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 將軍玉子漢堡<br />\n2. 新年出個 黃金招財福寶  <br />\n為咗食到塊薯餅<br />\n3. 仲有澳式芝蛋  右邊個個 要多醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/event/w600/201610/20161013155902_0_Angus_Beef_Burgers_with_Aussie_Breeze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fevent%2Fw600%2F201610%2F20161013155902_0_Angus_Beef_Burgers_with_Aussie_Breeze.jpg&h=ece04d89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cba190bb73f7e4084a4bf88763865f8bc8328556","tid":435470,"uid":2161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:06:52.000Z","msg":"1.將軍漢堡<br />\n2.豬柳蛋漢堡<br />\n3. 魚柳包"},{"pid":"d4aca872475444a20a267a68826100b3dfe5b8b9","tid":435470,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"足三兩<br />\n將軍漢堡<br />\n板燒雞"},{"pid":"65e749eda16e57cbd05dbe6ca89a7625c1b6ffc9","tid":435470,"uid":1997,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:11:22.000Z","msg":"板燒雞&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;ALL"},{"pid":"86c3def80048380498bb7a3a09779acfe2543d8e","tid":435470,"uid":72943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"板雞+招財雞&gt;脆辣雞腿包&gt;大雞"},{"pid":"40ed653dc6f36ac66d44eb2245a8d790beb844ab","tid":435470,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"